item.title: CVE-2024-3505|2024-07-03T18:27:22.109Z -- jfrog -- artifactory%20self-hosted
item.description: JFrog Artifactory Self-Hosted versions below 7.77.3, are vulnerable to sensitive information disclosure whereby a low-privileged authenticated user can read the proxy configuration. This does not affect JFrog cloud deployments.
